{"tid":2036694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[5.27] 切忌英雄主義 聽日唔係endgame","createTime":"2020-05-26T15:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T15:36:47.000Z","uid":21212,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"785f6f9a50c45b633eada92fda2e55347533c810","tid":2036694,"uid":21212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:23:03.000Z","msg":"►【戰略 + 戰術】527 527，人人都講527，你估人人都知527係做乜鳩咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2036593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2036593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n諗清楚聽日想做啲咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2036316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2036316</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n聽日有活動就大家都知<br />\n但想出金鐘既手足諗清楚 係咪真係要去<br />\n上面兩個post已經講得好detail 聽日點解不宜去金鐘<br />\n聽日目標好簡單 就係話比全世界知 香港人仲未放棄 抗爭唔會停<br />\n如果因為聽日想話俾人知自己有做嘢 而夾硬去金鐘 set兩三個rb 然後比狗咬 係咪真係值得？個rb喺路面幾分鐘就比人清啦 你威幾分鐘 換嚟代價幾大 自己諗<br />\n有手足話塞鐵都有風險 因為好多便衣 個人都唔建議用任何<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非法</span></span>方式塞鐵 <br />\n最後其實係想討論開花 <br />\n個人認為係最有可能 <br />\n因為狗力一定係相對少 <br />\n同埋大家可以快閃 <br />\n如果大家都覺得係既 快啲upvote呢個post 推上去 detail繼續討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：本人絕不鼓勵任何違法行為"},{"pid":"013dedbaa24b78e2a71887f1182c97d1670952f4","tid":2036694,"uid":21212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fc420c156220e1ade5f8e3e179f7df6905ba3564","tid":2036694,"uid":349945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"聽日唔係end game"},{"pid":"dc9f20fc73100d645a9beebcca8656f934663ad5","tid":2036694,"uid":21212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:28:38.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"5c1819be6f3db5121189fbe630158b1c3762ed00","tid":2036694,"uid":21212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:29:12.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"da694ea4636daeaafad7d6434f026ff0665aa806","tid":2036694,"uid